casebody.data:
Wednesday, February 15, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

95-268. No. 94CAH07018. In re Petition for Annexation of 941.3 Acres. Delaware County,

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and the same hereby is, granted, effective February 14, 1995, pending further order of this court.
